OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry and bright start for most
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells, the best of these
OL,7,Ftowards the coast where it will be
OL,8,Fwarmer than recent days. Cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing across southern and western
OL,10,FAberdeenshire for the afternoon with
OL,11,Foccasional rain. Fresh southwesterly
OL,12,Fwinds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSouth and west cloudy at
OL,15,Ffirst with patchy rain, otherwise a
OL,16,Fdry evening with some late sunny
OL,17,Fspells. Largely clear through early
OL,18,Fhours but becoming cloudy with some
OL,19,Frain later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
