OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, heaviest and most
OL,7,Fpersistent across western parts
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon. The rain turns
OL,9,Fmore showery later with a risk of
OL,10,Fthunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,13,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,14,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,15,FMainly dry and bright Monday with
OL,16,Fsunny spells, but cloudier Tuesday
OL,17,Fwith rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
